track.name: Girl of My Dreams
comments: This makes me feel sooo good! My tail tells me so!
The Monsters Inc. opening song sounds like this, in parts.
I was a Mingus fan while he was still alive. Missed a chance to see him live once.
I love this stuff live, but rarely can I listen to it throughout the day for fun.
I just love each and every song on this album but this one is something else. Excellent arrangement by Mingus and superb composition by Sonny Clapp.
Mingus is one of the finest jazz composers ever. Love the weird tempo changes in this one
Sempre grandissimo, qualsiasi album si ascolti si resta sempre incantati dalla sua carica di erotismo
